                                     lupkg

This is still a work in progress, but the goal is to have a simple packaging
tool to group deps together in a single executable.

BUILD REQUIREMENTS

* mksquashfs

RUNTIME REQUIREMENTS

* fusermount

INSTALLING

make
sudo make install

USAGE

mkdir myproject
cd ./myproject
lupkg init
lupkg build
sudo ./build/app.lupkg

# edit ./app/init, add files, etc...

lupkg build

# run the package
./build/app.lupkg

